  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Farring\" title=\"House Farring\"><img alt=\"House Farring.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e2/House_Farring.svg/50px-House_Farring.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e2/House_Farring.svg/75px-House_Farring.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e2/House_Farring.svg/100px-House_Farring.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lady</span><br />Annara Farring</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/50px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/75px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/100px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Annara_Farring_by_Helaenarts.jpeg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Annara Farring by Helaenarts.jpeg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0e/Annara_Farring_by_Helaenarts.jpeg/350px-Annara_Farring_by_Helaenarts.jpeg\" width=\"350\" height=\"357\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0e/Annara_Farring_by_Helaenarts.jpeg/525px-Annara_Farring_by_Helaenarts.jpeg 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0e/Annara_Farring_by_Helaenarts.jpeg/700px-Annara_Farring_by_Helaenarts.jpeg 2x\" /></a><div>Annara Farring, by Helaenarts ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nLady of the <a href=\"/index.php/Crossing\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Crossing\">Crossing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Farring\" title=\"House Farring\">House Farring</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n~<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_240_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">240</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_273_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">273&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-ages_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-ages-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_292_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">292</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-ages_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-ages-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Arwyn_Frey\" title=\"Arwyn Frey\">Arwyn Frey</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Wendel_Frey\" title=\"Wendel Frey\">Wendel Frey</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Colmar_Frey\" title=\"Colmar Frey\">Colmar Frey</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Waltyr_Frey\" title=\"Waltyr Frey\">Waltyr Frey</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Elmar_Frey\" title=\"Elmar Frey\">Elmar Frey</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Shirei_Frey\" title=\"Shirei Frey\">Shirei Frey</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Annara Farring</b> was a noblewoman of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Farring\" title=\"House Farring\">House Farring</a>, and the seventh wife of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a>. They had six children. She is deceased.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Annara_Farring&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Though invited to the wedding of Annara and Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> did not attend.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Rumors around the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a> claim that Annara may have been sleeping with Walder's great-grandson, <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey_(son_of_Ryman)\" title=\"Walder Frey (son of Ryman)\">Black Walder Frey</a>, casting doubts on her children's parentage.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Annara_Farring&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey_(son_of_Ryman)\" title=\"Walder Frey (son of Ryman)\">Black Walder</a> was a man who took what he wanted, even <a href=\"/index.php/Mylenda_Caron\" title=\"Mylenda Caron\">his brother's wife</a>. He'd had <a href=\"/index.php/Janyce_Hunter\" title=\"Janyce Hunter\">Edwyn's wife</a> too, that was common knowledge, <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Walton)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Walton)\">Fair Walda</a> had been known to slip into his bed from time to time, and some even said he'd known the seventh Lady Frey a deal better than he should have.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosepilogue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Merrett_Frey\" title=\"Merrett Frey\">Merrett Frey</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Annara_Farring&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Annara<br />Farring</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</s